OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fcontinue through the evening,
OL,7,Fgenerally becoming light and more
OL,8,Fisolated although the odd heavier
OL,9,Fburst still possible. Showers easing
OL,10,Foff around midnight with some clear
OL,11,Fspells developing and feeling cold.
OL,12,FLight winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FBright spells and frequent
OL,15,Fshowers through the day, some of which
OL,16,Fare likely to be heavy and thundery.
OL,17,FClouding over from the west overnight
OL,18,Fas rain and stronger winds arrive.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
